      "Add sliced onion and cook until slightly soft.",
      "Add turmeric, red chili powder, and salt. Mix well.",
      "Spread the thin potato slices in a single layer on the tava. Let them cook undisturbed for 3-4 minutes until crispy on one side.",
      "Flip gently and cook the other side until golden and crispy.",
      "Garnish with coriander leaves and serve hot with poli."
